=Episode 6=

3
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:42,040
(This drama is purely fictional.)

4
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:56,720
Are you really too idle?

5
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,420
You don't like him bothering Mi Lan.

6
00:01:58,650 --> 00:02:00,570
Why don't you just kill him
and be done with it?

7
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,720
Why all this fuss?

8
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:04,920
I'm no match for God.

9
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:06,690
God forbids me from being a human.

10
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,600
Fighting human

11
00:02:09,950 --> 00:02:11,670
requires human methods.

12
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:13,670
Besides,

13
00:02:14,110 --> 00:02:15,390
I find

14
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,880
Li Yingliang interesting.

15
00:02:19,990 --> 00:02:21,160
Wait for me in the car.

16
00:02:49,990 --> 00:02:51,200
Mr. Shen.

17
00:02:51,510 --> 00:02:52,390
What a rare guest.

18
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:03,880
Mr. Li.

19
00:03:04,510 --> 00:03:05,990
Aren't you going to invite me in?

20
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,600
I'd have it no other way.

21
00:03:07,950 --> 00:03:09,080
Mr. Shen, this way, please.

22
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:15,110
I came prepared this time.

23
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,600
After you go in,

24
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:19,790
I'll kill you if you play any tricks.

25
00:03:20,270 --> 00:03:23,040
Do you need these people
if you want to kill me?

26
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,080
Mr. Shen, please.

27
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:46,640
So this guy is Li Yingliang.

28
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,230
He's nothing.

29
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,950
Mr. Shen, I'm pleasantly surprised

30
00:03:57,950 --> 00:03:59,390
that you took the time to come today.

31
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:01,200
I thought you resented me.

32
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:03,950
I didn't get a chance to make peace
and clear up the misunderstanding.

33
00:04:05,230 --> 00:04:07,390
Making peace or not is between us.

34
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:10,480
You shouldn't have
encouraged Miss Mi to persuade me.

35
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:13,360
She's young and has trouble moving around.

36
00:04:14,850 --> 00:04:16,440
That's taking advantage of her, isn't it?

37
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:19,000
Are you here to question me?

38
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,200
Mr. Shen.

39
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:32,240
It's rare for us to sit here
and talk calmly.

40
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:33,830
I've done something cruel to you.

41
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,390
You didn't spare me either.

42
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,390
You're lucky you're not dead.

43
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,120
I'm lucky I didn't die.

44
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:43,000
God has arranged for us
to sit here and talk.

45
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,560
I think we should just accept

46
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,830
and cherish this opportunity.

47
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:49,350
You've seen my attitude these days.

48
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:52,440
I really tried to get close to you,

49
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,320
but you didn't give me the chance.

50
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:57,510
I had no choice but to go to Miss Mi.

51
00:04:57,880 --> 00:05:00,950
I know Miss Mi is important to you.

52
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,150
She saved you.

53
00:05:02,590 --> 00:05:05,320
I just wanted Miss Mi
to pass you a message for me.

54
00:05:05,710 --> 00:05:08,270
I didn't mean to intimidate
or threaten you in any way.

55
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:12,070
Besides, why should I scare a little girl?

56
00:05:13,710 --> 00:05:15,320
You got it wrong.

57
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,470
It's not that she saved me.

58
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:19,150
I saved her.

59
00:05:19,470 --> 00:05:22,630
Without me, she would have died
in the hospital.

60
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:25,150
You're right.

61
00:05:25,590 --> 00:05:28,570
She would have died
if you hadn't taken care of her.

62
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,800
And if she hadn't saved you that night,

63
00:05:32,470 --> 00:05:33,920
you could have survived too, right?

64
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:43,000
Don't get me wrong.

65
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,710
I'm just being honest.

66
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,560
I meant no harm.

67
00:05:51,030 --> 00:05:51,880
Mr. Shen.

68
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,560
Can you tell me if you...

69
00:05:58,760 --> 00:05:59,950
Why you...

70
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,120
What I'm saying is...

71
00:06:06,590 --> 00:06:07,880
Logically speaking,

72
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,120
you should be dead that night.

73
00:06:10,590 --> 00:06:13,000
But how did you come back safe and sound

74
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,470
after vanishing for ten days?

75
00:06:14,470 --> 00:06:15,470
You didn't die.

76
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:17,560
Why?

77
00:06:19,470 --> 00:06:20,510
Do you want to know why?

78
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:27,510
I swear what you tell me today

79
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,190
will be kept strictly confidential.

80
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,880
If I violate this oath,

81
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:33,880
I will be struck by lightning,
have no children,

82
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:37,800
go to hell, and never be reincarnated.

83
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:44,470
How could Mr. Li
curse himself like this?

84
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,920
Mr. Shen, don't get me wrong.

85
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,800
There's no ambush here.

86
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,630
They all obey my orders.

87
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:03,760
Actually, I'm a monster.

88
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,150
No.

89
00:07:13,030 --> 00:07:14,800
Mr. Shen, can you stop messing with me?

90
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,470
I even swore a solemn oath.

91
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,760
You told me you're a monster.

92
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:20,510
You're too unserious.

93
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,320
I'm really a monster.

94
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,470
Come to my house tonight
if you don't believe me.

95
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,470
I'll show you what I am.

96
00:07:30,710 --> 00:07:31,390
I wouldn't dare.

97
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:39,000
It's a good thing to be cautious.

98
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,390
Better safe than sorry.

99
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,710
But don't worry.

100
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,390
You can get your promotion
while I make my money.

101
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,510
If we don't stand in each other's way,

102
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,800
I won't hurt you.

103
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:53,200
But if you can't control your curiosity,

104
00:07:54,470 --> 00:07:58,360
don't blame me for being impulsive.

105
00:08:01,150 --> 00:08:02,950
It doesn't matter who I am.

106
00:08:05,030 --> 00:08:08,880
What matters is whether you can live well.

107
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:13,000
Mr. Shen, are you here to warn me today?

108
00:08:19,030 --> 00:08:20,920
I'm not that kind.

109
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:24,270
I never give warnings.

110
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:27,030
If I warn you, won't you be wary?

111
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,320
I'm not that foolish.

112
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,040
Well... Mr. Shen.

113
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,920
Can I treat you to dinner?

114
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:42,110
It's late.

115
00:08:42,110 --> 00:08:43,110
The time is just right.

116
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,630
I don't eat food.

117
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,040
I eat people.

118
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,110
Please escort me out.

119
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,350
Don't hold Mr. Li Hostage again.

120
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,160
Shut up.

121
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,860
Put the gun down.

122
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,440
What's your name?

123
00:09:02,990 --> 00:09:03,990
My name is Li Guisheng.

124
00:09:03,990 --> 00:09:04,690
What's the matter?

125
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:05,970
Come at me if you need anything.

126
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:07,950
I'll remember you.

127
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:09,750
Mr...

128
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,230
Mr. Shen.

129
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,040
I think we need to talk.

130
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,230
Superintendent Chi
would love to be your friend.

131
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,990
And I would love to...

132
00:09:16,990 --> 00:09:18,110
Shut up!

133
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:48,590
Mr. Li.

134
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:51,560
Let's not see each other again
after today.

135
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,080
Otherwise...

136
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:55,680
I'll eat you up.

137
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,320
Scumbag.

138
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,040
How dare he scold you like that?

139
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:25,950
What's so weird about that?

140
00:10:31,990 --> 00:10:33,320
He can even kill me.

141
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:36,870
Well...

142
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,590
Are we still following him?

143
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:40,520
Follow him?

144
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:46,870
Disperse.

145
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:57,710
What happened to you?

146
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,680
Help me come up with a solution.

147
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,230
Li Yingliang
discovered my relationship with her

148
00:11:04,470 --> 00:11:05,520
and wants to go after her.

149
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,110
It's inconvenient for her
to go out and be seen now.

150
00:11:08,470 --> 00:11:09,710
If she stays at home,

151
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:12,040
I'm afraid Mrs. Mi
will continue to abuse her.

152
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,320
I have a good idea.

153
00:11:17,620 --> 00:11:26,220
(Shen Mansion)

154
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,680
No!

155
00:11:42,350 --> 00:11:43,230
I won't do it.

156
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:44,800
- Don't run. Come back.
- Stop following me.

157
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,680
We're not done.

158
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,400
Stop following me.

159
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,560
One last bit.

160
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:49,680
Let me finish.

161
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:51,590
No.

162
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:52,680
- Last one. Stop.
- Stop.

163
00:11:53,250 --> 00:11:55,180
You're an adult.
How can you be afraid of this?

164
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,630
You know, right?

165
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,680
You know I'm actually quite old.

166
00:11:58,990 --> 00:12:00,830
It's fine. You look young.

167
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:04,280
After all, I'm a newspaper tycoon
and a Haidong dignitary.

168
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,950
I've been respectable
for over a hundred years.

169
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:09,400
How can you make me do such a thing?

170
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:11,350
Didn't you want a permanent solution?

171
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:13,040
Look at how good this is.

172
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:15,350
As humans, let's do it the way humans do it.

173
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:17,710
You'll look ugly,
but it will be good for Miss Mi.

174
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:20,470
But this is so ugly.

175
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:21,560
Stop nagging.

176
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:22,750
Or it'll be dawn soon.

177
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:24,390
Will you let me draw or not?

178
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:25,870
No way.

179
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:12,350
Mr. Shen, is it you?

180
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:22,470
I knew you would see me.

181
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,470
Did she hit you again?

182
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:29,320
She drank too much last night,

183
00:13:30,350 --> 00:13:31,470
but I dodged her.

184
00:13:31,470 --> 00:13:32,690
So I didn't get any serious injuries.

185
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,630
I promised you that you
would have nothing to worry about.

186
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:37,680
As a result,

187
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:39,190
Li Yingliang came to you because of me.

188
00:13:39,950 --> 00:13:40,990
I don't mind.

189
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,680
He knows no boundaries.

190
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,680
If we keep seeing each other,

191
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:46,110
he'll keep coming to you.

192
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,520
You'll be in danger.

193
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:50,470
I'll find a way to get your mother
to stop bothering you.

194
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:54,560
You can keep going to choir.

195
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:56,870
Mr. Shen.

196
00:13:58,710 --> 00:14:00,280
Are you bidding me goodbye?

197
00:14:03,470 --> 00:14:04,590
It's just temporary.

198
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:07,320
I have to solve some things first

199
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:09,400
if I want you to live a normal life.

200
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:13,120
But this is normal to me.

201
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:14,630
It's not normal, Mi Lan.

202
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:17,350
No one is in danger every day.

203
00:14:17,350 --> 00:14:20,400
And no one gets beaten
and scolded by their mother all the time.

204
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:21,950
I'm not scared.

205
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:23,830
But I can't allow it.

206
00:14:49,590 --> 00:14:50,710
Mr. Shen.

207
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,400
Why are you wearing a veil?

208
00:14:53,710 --> 00:14:54,800
Are you injured?

209
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,350
Yes.

210
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:00,110
I didn't want to scare you.

211
00:15:00,950 --> 00:15:02,110
I can't see.

212
00:15:05,350 --> 00:15:06,400
You're right.

213
00:15:06,990 --> 00:15:08,040
I forgot.

214
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:11,950
Mr. Shen.

215
00:15:12,710 --> 00:15:14,160
You must live well.

216
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,590
Don't let bad guys hurt you again.

217
00:15:18,110 --> 00:15:20,750
I promise you I'll live well.

218
00:15:23,110 --> 00:15:24,280
Take good care of yourself.

219
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:33,200
Where is your mother's bedroom?

220
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:35,040
Second floor.

221
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:38,590
What's the matter?

222
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,440
Nothing.

223
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,750
I'll talk to her.

224
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:44,950
You should go to bed soon.

225
00:15:45,710 --> 00:15:46,280
Go.

226
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:48,680
Hurry.

227
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:34,040
Shut up.

228
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:39,440
I'm the Mi family's ancestor.

229
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:42,680
You wicked wench.

230
00:16:42,990 --> 00:16:46,080
Do you know what you did wrong?

231
00:17:05,870 --> 00:17:08,760
You torture the Mi family's descendant
day and night.

232
00:17:08,910 --> 00:17:14,720
I came back to life today
just to take your life.

233
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:19,720
I'm sorry.

234
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:22,910
Since you're the mother
of the Mi family's descendant,

235
00:17:23,080 --> 00:17:27,150
I'll spare your life if you repent.

236
00:17:27,150 --> 00:17:29,430
I'm willing to repent.

237
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:34,320
If you commit the same offense again,

238
00:17:34,430 --> 00:17:37,870
I'll take you to
the Mi family's ancestors

239
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:41,350
to suffer in hell.

240
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:43,100
I won't do it anymore.

241
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:46,350
I won't do it. I won't do it anymore.

242
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:47,910
I'll never do it anymore.

243
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:24,280
- Madam.
- Madam.

244
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:26,080
Madam, how are you?

245
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:28,350
Did you have a nightmare, Madam?

246
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,190
Are you all right?

247
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:30,960
Go get a glass of water.

248
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:31,580
I'll get the towel.

249
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:33,080
Madam.

250
00:18:33,390 --> 00:18:34,150
Are you okay?

251
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,870
Are you okay? Let me see, Madam.

252
00:18:36,670 --> 00:18:37,800
Madam, how are you?

253
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:38,870
Madam.

254
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:02,350
Madam, you can't drink any more.

255
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:03,390
No.

256
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:05,150
I can't sleep without drinking.

257
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:07,870
Our family is considered lucky.

258
00:19:08,280 --> 00:19:09,320
I heard a few days ago

259
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:11,080
that there's a beast attack

260
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,590
that even killed someone.

261
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,830
It was on the news.

262
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:15,800
I heard it was scary.

263
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,500
Just like a monster.

264
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:18,150
Stop!

265
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:19,870
Madam Xu.

266
00:19:19,870 --> 00:19:21,520
Madam Xu, what do I do? Save me.

267
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:23,350
Help me. I'm scared.

268
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,910
Calm down.

269
00:19:24,910 --> 00:19:25,770
Where are you going?

270
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:32,870
Madam, don't be scared.

271
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:35,560
I heard
that monsters are afraid of strong men.

272
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:37,080
Let him stand guard at your door.

273
00:19:37,430 --> 00:19:39,590
Madam, I'll protect you.

274
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,110
I'm here, Madam.

275
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:31,560
Come in.

276
00:20:51,670 --> 00:20:53,000
Newspaper for sale!

277
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:54,480
Breaking news!

278
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,560
Mrs. Mi eloped with someone.

279
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,260
Newspaper for sale!

