You'll feel hungry if you don't eat.

559
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,790
You haven't eaten for a day.

560
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,510
What should you do
if you starve yourself?

561
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:55,480
Li Yingliang.

562
00:36:56,520 --> 00:36:58,310
I'll cooperate this time.

563
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:00,960
But you have to think carefully

564
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:03,790
about whether you can really
put me in prison forever.

565
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:05,310
If you can't...

566
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:27,690
The last time
he was at Dongya Restaurant,

567
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:28,790
he didn't eat either.

568
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:31,750
I thought he was afraid
I'd poison his food.

569
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:33,630
Now it seems

570
00:37:33,630 --> 00:37:35,750
that he's afraid I'd poison him

571
00:37:36,190 --> 00:37:37,520
or he can't eat.

572
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:40,670
Mr. Li.

573
00:37:41,590 --> 00:37:43,440
Isn't it normal for us

574
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:46,560
to put him in jail
for three or four days without food?

575
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:48,300
No.

576
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:50,370
We must find a way
to make him reveal his true form.

577
00:37:50,790 --> 00:37:53,040
If he makes it out alive,

578
00:37:53,790 --> 00:37:55,440
I'll die.

579
00:37:58,520 --> 00:38:00,110
Mr. Li, this is the observation record.

580
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,440
(Not scared of the cold.)

581
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:10,000
(Afraid of heat.)

582
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:12,750
Food is served.

583
00:38:20,560 --> 00:38:22,480
Miss Mi, take your time.

584
00:38:22,590 --> 00:38:24,150
I need to check the kitchen.

585
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:32,310
Did you know
that Mr. Shen was taken away?

586
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:34,270
Mr. Shen was taken away?

587
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,080
Yeah.

588
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:36,190
The news has got abroad.

589
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,480
Mr. Shen committed a crime

590
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:39,920
and was taken from Shen Mansion
yesterday afternoon.

591
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:41,150
He still hasn't come out.

592
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:42,290
What are you talking about?

593
00:38:45,630 --> 00:38:47,160
What did you say happened to Mr. Shen?

594
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:47,960
Miss Mi.

595
00:38:48,300 --> 00:38:50,670
I only heard that he committed a crime
and was taken away.

596
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:51,670
Where was he taken?

597
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,360
I don't know where he was taken.

598
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:54,920
The police took him away.

599
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,700
He's probably at the police station.

600
00:38:58,980 --> 00:39:00,230
Miss Mi.

601
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:02,000
Miss Mi.

602
00:39:24,270 --> 00:39:25,840
We tried everything.

603
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:29,000
We did the most unthinkable things,

604
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:31,360
but nothing changed.

605
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:34,710
Does he have too much self-control,

606
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:40,840
or he lied about him being a monster?

607
00:39:41,960 --> 00:39:43,480
I don't eat food.

608
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,590
I eat people.

609
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:51,040
Or does he really eat people?

610
00:39:53,110 --> 00:39:54,080
We can't believe that.

611
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:55,670
He said that to scare you.

612
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:57,110
It's fake.

613
00:39:57,750 --> 00:39:58,590
I have no choice.

614
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:01,590
I'm doomed if I can't complete
Superintendent Chi's order.

615
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:04,560
If Shen Zhiheng comes out alive,
I'm also doomed.

616
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:07,960
Then...

617
00:40:08,750 --> 00:40:09,840
I'll think of a way.

618
00:40:10,670 --> 00:40:11,110
You...

619
00:40:12,670 --> 00:40:15,270
You'll give me trouble if you do this.

620
00:40:15,270 --> 00:40:16,080
Chief Lin.

621
00:40:16,310 --> 00:40:18,080
When you accepted my case,

622
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:20,590
we're in this together.

623
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:21,560
No, you... I...

624
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:25,000
Don't worry.
This is Superintendent Chi's order.

625
00:41:02,710 --> 00:41:03,880
What's the meaning of this?

626
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:06,270
So you're awake.

627
00:41:06,700 --> 00:41:09,640
I saw that you're not eating or drinking
and was worried I mistreated you.

628
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:11,040
I went back and thought about it.

629
00:41:11,190 --> 00:41:12,480
I'm indeed a bad host.

630
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:14,080
You said

631
00:41:14,230 --> 00:41:15,790
you don't eat food and only eat people.

632
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,750
So I went down to the dungeon

633
00:41:17,750 --> 00:41:19,190
and picked out a death row prisoner.

634
00:41:19,230 --> 00:41:19,840
Don't worry.

635
00:41:20,230 --> 00:41:22,520
He has no father, no mother,
no wife, and no daughter.

636
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:24,560
You can eat him.

637
00:41:25,110 --> 00:41:26,750
No one knows he's dead.

638
00:42:05,651 --> 00:42:10,131
♪Of all the marks imprinted in my heart♪

639
00:42:11,071 --> 00:42:15,851
♪People come and go,
the weather is ever-changing♪

640
00:42:16,651 --> 00:42:21,611
♪Endless expectations and reminiscing♪

641
00:42:21,851 --> 00:42:26,661
♪Having no say in one's will♪

642
00:42:26,771 --> 00:42:27,701
♪Oh♪

643
00:42:28,051 --> 00:42:30,201
♪On the same path♪

644
00:42:30,791 --> 00:42:33,201
♪With different burdens♪

645
00:42:33,291 --> 00:42:35,351
♪And different destinations♪

646
00:42:37,721 --> 00:42:38,781
♪Oh♪

647
00:42:39,021 --> 00:42:41,461
♪Different steps♪

648
00:42:41,791 --> 00:42:44,101
♪Pursuing the same goal♪

649
00:42:44,511 --> 00:42:47,481
♪With different sense of belonging♪

650
00:42:51,531 --> 00:42:54,171
♪Oh, I see the exit♪

651
00:42:54,561 --> 00:42:56,801
♪Hey, there's no end to this♪

652
00:42:56,951 --> 00:43:02,571
♪A soul that has found its home,
devoting everything to love♪

653
00:43:02,591 --> 00:43:05,221
♪Oh, reasons that can be articulated♪

654
00:43:05,331 --> 00:43:07,861
♪Hey, can't escape
from the ridiculousness♪

655
00:43:08,041 --> 00:43:15,901
♪Destiny is a maze where those inside
are interconnected♪

656
00:43:38,391 --> 00:43:41,031
♪Oh, have you possessed it before?♪

657
00:43:41,171 --> 00:43:43,591
♪Hey, have you stayed true
to someone before?♪

658
00:43:43,771 --> 00:43:49,441
♪A soul that can't find its home
is still searching♪

659
00:43:49,521 --> 00:43:52,151
♪Oh, it's too late to fabricate♪

660
00:43:52,191 --> 00:43:54,791
♪Hey, it's too late to wave♪

661
00:43:54,951 --> 00:44:01,601
♪Fate disregards all reasons,
putting right and wrong together♪
